    "en": {
      "title": "Alcohol fight: Corpse in the rectum",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Maharagama Police have arrested a man suspected of assaulting and killing a Paco motorist at a Navinna holiday hotel in Maharagama and hiding him in a latrine.",
        "The deceased was identified as A., 37, of Harantota, Ratnapura. H. He has been identified as Ravindra.",
        "Police said the incident took place following an argument between the suspect and the murdered man after drinking alcohol.",
        "The arrested suspect is a 42 year old from Katugasthota area and police are conducting further investigations."
      ],
